    "title": "Entry-Level SEO Specialist at Tata CLiQ",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Tata CLiQ. We are on the lookout for a dedicated SEO Specialist to strengthen our Noida-based team.\n\nAbout Tata CLiQ:\nTata CLiQ is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tata CLiQ!",
